```coq
Inductive Ens : Type := 
  | sup : forall A : Type, (A -> Ens) -> Ens.

Fixpoint INC (E1 E2 : Ens) : Prop :=
  match E1 with 
  | sup A f => 
     forall E : Ens, IN E E1 -> IN E E2
  end.

Lemma INC_sound_left : 
  forall E E' E'' : Ens, EQ E E' -> INC E E'' -> INC E' E''.
Proof.
  intros E E' E'' H H0.
  unfold INC in H0.
  destruct E; simpl in *; auto.
Qed.

Lemma INC_sound_right : 
  forall E E' E'' : Ens, EQ E' E'' -> INC E E' -> INC E E''.
Proof.
  intros E E' E'' H H0.
  unfold INC in H0.
  destruct E; simpl in *; auto.
Qed.

Lemma INC_tran : 
  forall E E' E'' : Ens, INC E E' -> INC E' E'' -> INC E E''.
Proof.
  intros E E' E'' H H0.
  unfold INC in H0.
  destruct E; simpl in *; auto.
Qed.

Theorem INC_EE : 
  forall E E' : Ens, INC E E' -> Prop.
Proof.
  intros E E' H.
  induction E as [|A f IH]; simpl; auto.
  apply INC_tran with E'.
  apply IH.
  apply INC_sound_left.
  apply INC_sound_right.
Qed.
```
